  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>표지 싸바리 박스</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d3bcc15d-d334-4429-9344-f3a360df2250\" style=\"color:#555555;\">는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bee83a80-aedf-4957-ad1c-df817875dca3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223955484780/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-caption\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5da4c10b-ca88-45cc-8c75-d8baed19d069\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-2c085bcb-1dfb-4446-a670-b7dcdf6a4079\" style=\"\">고객과의 협의가 되지 않아 모자이크 처리함</span></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-7350edcb-30cb-4bbd-ab87-5a1f99926fb7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e8abbcd6-6939-49d5-9eb7-725d2a5e290c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-91b45a36-9c5d-4d71-af05-ceaf22deb1c6\" style=\"\">표지 싸바리 박스</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dff02985-e4f6-4c80-864d-f30918e1f253\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6ea0cb2d-55d4-4aa9-9bc7-ea9ea3e13043\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-026734ee-65a0-406d-87b9-17c61dc1e23a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">표지 싸바리 박스는 정면에 자석이 달려서 여닫을 수 있는 상자를 말합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f27e2518-53fd-463f-8d07-97400f4abd71\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223955484780/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ef760e53-45dc-4a72-b0d0-54b1b69a3324\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-960e2fd4-dc83-4185-b051-33781e077735\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e8b36be1-aefa-43f9-906d-91df8f940c5a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">자석이 붙어있는 면과 안쪽의 면지 부분이 있습니다. 그리고 박스 하단에 합지하는 공간이 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1683922e-8b42-44bf-8832-88690a3b8279\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e4c42797-1f6f-4475-b3f8-cb0cefe3ab8c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ed88e74a-3456-4be1-9ab8-2db0a7a025ff\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8481bcf2-adb7-4e5f-9730-d74b1be05a07\" style=\"color:#555555;\">대부분의 인쇄면은 표지바리 상단과 안쪽의 면지에 인쇄를 하게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8e05b85b-8c27-46cc-8959-2cd2f5090324\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7071167a-a680-4627-a355-6c28d839b300\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9ee5b2d5-1d41-49f7-a0a2-2ea2cb4acf14\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4a1cdfad-115f-4c0a-9d5a-f2022415dd95\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이번 샘플 작업은 다음과 같은 사양으로 제작되었습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-0e7cb56d-32b1-473d-9aae-c71e7cb2d680\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-943d7e02-4560-4558-9168-e1894c15b9b5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-e312345e-f767-4334-94ba-393a11aa3c93\" style=\"\">표지 싸바리 샘플 제작 사양</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-57a7d18e-8dce-4902-9b55-fc68e868ba8b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-508b687b-8187-48fb-ada0-99eb71fa05a4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-188f9c27-ab56-47d4-854f-687dc901a251\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>모든 인쇄면의 별색인쇄 + 컬러 4도 인쇄</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-198fcacf-c102-47e4-883c-6cba862e099f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ae37df6e-3942-4ac9-8367-11ee83b3ef5a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-33e15ea8-ed4f-416b-b0af-bbd3d9d683ab\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c31396c7-b850-4c43-b0af-1fc280d9677e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이번 샘플 작업은 에르메스 계열의 주황색 별색을 추가하여 작업하였습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-slide\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-imageGroup se-l-slide\" id=\"SE-69191ccb-13c8-4514-ac8e-02b056a9758b\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-viewer\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-container\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223955484780/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223955484780/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation\">\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-prev\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Previous image</span></button>\n<button class=\"se-imageGroup-navigation-button se-imageGroup-navigation-button-next\" type=\"button\"><span class=\"se-blind\">Next image</span></button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-progress\"><div class=\"se-imageGroup-thumb\"></div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3a7be68e-66e1-444d-a19d-f919795c6a58\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4bd8fea5-2087-4f36-bd94-f5c7ed9e458d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e1a42ed6-b8fb-4fa6-a225-0e3a1ce13266\" style=\"color:#555555;\">별색을 베다로 찍지는 않고 4도 인쇄가 되는 부분을 파내서 작업하였습니다. 별색과 4도가 겹치게 되면 색상이 변질될 수 있습니다. 물론 더 정확하게 핀트를 맞춰서 흰색 부분이 보이지 않게 작업하는 것이 중요합니다. 이 부분이 궁금하시면 언제든지 문의하여 주시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5cc96007-3ca5-4c44-9dd7-304575271ea7\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-082e7347-9b96-4174-9cfb-818f2b0c8a0a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cf52ba5c-c84d-49b6-b1ec-6a9e63101ebd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-087be9a4-a989-47d8-9e81-1f0c4257252e\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">별색을 사용하는 이유는 여러 가지가 있지만 가장 큰 이유는 색상의 통일성입니다. 통일성이란 4도 인쇄로 주황색을 구현하다 보면 최초 인쇄장과 끝장이 달라질 수 있습니다. 또는 발주시마다 색상이 조금씩 달라질 수 있습니다. 이런 부분을 보완하기 위해 별색을 따로 만들어서 그 조합된 별색으로만 진행하게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1ec75180-03e0-41bc-9862-f4310b3668d9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-83cc9911-48bd-445a-b497-e3638c84fbb7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-971b8af3-8c7d-4a84-bbe1-67e10f1f019d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c242837c-344c-4511-9e55-8c6e4286159e\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>상짝 부분에 유광 금박</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6fcd9d33-6839-4baa-9dbd-d7db0264e1bf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4522e7b9-dc5f-40e0-8daa-6dcbce00c4d0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-157e78a6-38c1-42cb-8ac2-c2a253bb6e47\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-04f1cb0a-8ba3-44a9-b8f5-a67350a09366\" style=\"color:#555555;\">샘플 작업임에도 박인쇄를 작업했습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-83093249-f4b7-4680-b8de-7798053491fe\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223955484780/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c32da35a-b142-4b7f-a3c2-8b03123b1841\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6d9d0101-e031-49bb-b887-aab69c67489f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fc9bb973-bd81-4235-b5c9-67ec1a4d44e8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">주황색에 유광 금박이 은은하게 잘 자리 잡고 멋지게 구현되었습니다. 앞쪽 자석에도 박인쇄 부분이 있어서 동판의 면적이 넓습니다. 이 비용을 감수하면서 박인쇄를 진행할 만큼 촬영용으로 최고의 샘플을 제작했다고 자부합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2d179830-9935-4a34-a313-a9dfb4aebd22\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1a59a60f-9f7f-448c-a545-cba247c74984\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c6c7eca0-cec8-4af5-94a1-a8200964628f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b9e34ffd-6463-428f-b3ca-3bd020f91554\" style=\"color:#555555;\">동판 비용은 무착이나 비쌉니다. 특히 면적당 계산을 하기 때문에 전체를 덮는 박인쇄라면 많은 비용이 나갑니다. 하지만 1회용으로 제작하는 아연판으로 제작할 수 있습니다. 여러 번 사용하면 마모되어 사용성이 덜어지지만 기존의 동판보다는 저렴하여 샘플용으로는 많이 사용되는 판입니다. 이번 샘플용으로는 아연판을 사용하였습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-177fc017-30a5-4d94-92be-dcda3b130e5f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-440960a6-8a16-4e25-9255-5ec3ef47ab64\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-01831753-c62c-459c-bef5-1da5862aa52b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b3ae78ee-153f-4c84-8dec-6d58dd951244\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>샘플러를 통한 커팅 작업</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d48cb79a-69fa-43d9-9cd1-6e37f3c6d0dd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a21f4e88-d7a7-498c-9426-d2c7abff928b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ed3c4e08-ebc3-4654-8a81-edb546b650e8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6ba2bad9-56e6-4d9b-a9eb-5556ec574615\" style=\"color:#555555;\">원래는 목형을 만들고 톰슨(도무송)작업을 해야 합니다. 하지만 샘플은 이런 목형을 만들고 작업하기가 쉽지 않습니다. 특히 종이 패드인 경우는 샘플을 보고 변경하거나 수정하는 경우가 많기 때문에 목형을 만드는 것이 부담이 될 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3b91c6f3-31ef-4939-84a0-06697ce7206d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223955484780/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8c198e97-e6ca-4bae-b0fc-cf9e21216b3d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-75ee6fc6-4144-46d3-bd8a-199c88595acc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9244dfa5-6c55-49bb-bc6e-cc2796aee341\" style=\"color:#555555;\">위 공진단이 들어가는 구멍이 60개가 들어 있습니다. 이 원을 목형 만든다면 원 하나당 칼 비용이 청구될 것입니다. 이 비용은 샘플로 만들기에는 부담이 되는 금액일 겁니다. 디지털 샘플러로 일단 제작을 진행합니다. 물론 목형보다는 거칠고 깔끔하게 제작되지는 않습니다. 이는 분명히 고객에게 고지하셔야 합니다. 저렴한 만큼 퀄리티는 목형 + 톰슨(도무송)보다 떨어진 다는 것을 이해하여 주셔야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bc6aabf2-95a4-45d9-8c65-935aedafdb36\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223955484780/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c6b1f73f-ef67-490a-8ffc-05f314b12b2b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1711ed12-940a-46df-a3ea-5497f3435574\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-df2c4d81-a12f-4ffc-ad9f-c3ed962e464a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-384796b7-94ad-41ae-a5fa-95fc314a8163\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-73534a45-05f9-4b36-a7d4-2e181c20eeae\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-eb890935-a72d-4629-9f63-a81798c2a3cf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a5b486d8-667f-403e-b441-66567bccf80a\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>앞쪽 자석 작업</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-da203572-1b07-4e6c-89cc-c2c6b2433d14\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-71e6e9d4-7f98-4584-a750-4cf9b491c419\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f57af852-d164-48da-b8f1-ec20a3b0206f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-806a57a5-a1f2-494b-a458-84133c4e96ef\" style=\"color:#555555;\">샘플에서도 자석을 삽입했습니다. 물론 소량이기 때문에 가능하지만 소량이기 때문에 거의 수작업으로 작업이 진행됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-79a8ad7e-dfd4-40c4-b487-92c19e997d40\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223955484780/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d6e20527-c11a-4dcf-b809-98d2b018d83e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1d0e01e6-8c9b-4cfa-8fe6-434c23e2fc8a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5e95e278-2c76-43fb-a0a5-16192aa2d352\" style=\"color:#555555;\">자석은 특별한 경우가 아니라면 양쪽에 원형 자석 2개를 부착합니다. 사이즈가 크거나 모양이 다르다면 사각 자석이나 통자석을 착용하는 경우도 있습니다. 하지만 일반적으로는 원형 자석 2개가 들어가게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-19194e2c-9992-4e95-b6be-ceb12aba997c\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c40950a5-6341-494a-97d2-f704c6dcee82\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3bfba550-bcbd-42a8-aee3-383cf38ecb91\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-844102fe-8db3-4c7c-a848-14a56b348e07\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>면지 인쇄 작업</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7f0070dd-14e5-4006-8630-dfb0353e7c1a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d371ed1c-cb83-4a20-9b56-daa7868b6a41\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bfb0f3ea-727d-4dd2-a897-3ded0c6cdc4f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d635199c-ac4d-4861-91fa-91615ade5207\" style=\"color:#555555;\">정면 뚜껑을 열었을 때의 면지에 인쇄하는 경우도 있습니다. 특히 표지 싸바리 박스의 경우는 대부분 인쇄가 들어갑니다. 면지에 인쇄를 하게 되면 면지 종이도 선택해야 하고 인쇄 방식도 정해야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-83baf83b-3772-404a-84aa-53db67bd4055\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223955484780/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-b67c19c2-b957-4547-9d00-e91e88a85edd\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-70388b2c-808e-4870-84ea-b6c96d1b06d9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-4ec68639-2999-40dc-90e3-debcec6148db\" style=\"\">표지 싸바리 박스 샘플</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-efb0a75a-890c-40ee-b433-ee148ef09554\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8a261dce-8dfc-4da9-99f1-7cf39696a090\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d973d49f-1385-4266-8823-410d16c2c867\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>종이</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4f838f66-2618-4188-91b7-eefc902c6dfd\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 편아트 120g + 1000DT 갱판지</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1319fa12-97d2-4f6c-83e5-d740f8cdffa0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5356c2f3-eede-41d6-9dd1-136445e1043d\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>종이 패드</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d65a1dcf-3fc1-4713-9ed4-027ad274ece8\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : E골 골판지</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bc2ac13d-e8d7-4b9c-8e5a-d03a399ac808\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-1605486e-348c-425a-a268-8dd3d44dcdfe\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>사이즈</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9969fd22-3328-4244-a696-ccce6b81bb16\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 250mm × 380mm × 60mm</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-63988c1f-0b68-4ebc-80de-f0fe17d3ae2c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-881404d0-c2e9-4589-bcb0-130928a5d9af\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>인쇄</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b7f47910-b80f-4610-b30b-6a820e235118\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 주황색 별색 + 4도 인쇄</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-868dfe19-a075-45ab-88a1-707816c723bd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-46dbecb4-7b05-46b5-a0cc-4896356e859a\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>면지 인쇄</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3772bfec-e802-44ff-a995-a37239d7a079\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 단면 4도 인쇄</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-919ec41e-9458-4367-8745-088f163addad\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-