e-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e2147aa5-5112-4357-b559-1913182043b0\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 샘플 2개</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-910d9fb9-aad5-455a-8b01-c12a587ed232\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-eb2705f4-6545-413f-860b-42d41ba831ed\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>납기</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f0816e96-f6e6-4c83-84fb-5ab3731fce11\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 발주 후 5일 (비즈니스 데이 기준)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-06ef689e-8afe-490b-9eb9-9e9d0c07e578\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-9fa5f957-6d30-4bdc-8276-7e78ce353a84\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>비용</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d59c6b79-fa66-4b52-91f3-223a2f2ccfc1\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 별도 문의</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ab9d47c0-0399-4915-b1af-7cef1deb291e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a2e805dd-1040-4c21-aa33-e3600ce71f40\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5a5df141-df21-46f8-9f95-426eeac716b0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8d160c7f-2c05-44dc-a55d-66fb2f42e112\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>본 작업</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-64cf242e-9e0d-405a-9348-e653e9c72acf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f2d4d064-81fa-4c52-bc17-6a21243e6e92\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>수량</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d2c526f5-f81a-430d-94cd-74bd8ead9682\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 1,000개</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b09a568b-c8fa-4024-85fe-cca9f0624a40\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-7939954a-3e3f-4804-a78a-3f7cd12f163c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>특기 : </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bde89668-f9fc-4148-b79c-8705e99faf24\" style=\"color:#555555;\">샘플과 동일한 사양으로 제작, 다만 하단에 스펀지 삽입 요청</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6882be1f-a51a-4db6-9ec1-c693b68bac06\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e8503a47-126f-493b-94de-c5be039ecc75\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-6fe38994-98f4-45cc-9df5-13125e9d9d8a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-87e4edd7-977d-4375-aaa5-bdb90fd1a78a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-6f63c4d4-45d8-4eaa-9416-be1b3392f900\" style=\"\">샘플 제작을 하는 경우</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-aed1f96f-b0f8-45ee-9103-d5d362e427b1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6a9a69e4-1e8e-4a60-a284-da79403b5ce5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3d8007ef-8c5b-422e-ae7e-76d6948c8513\" style=\"color:#555555;\">비용을 주고 샘플을 제작하는 경우는 샘플을 보고 색상이나 상황을 판단하기 의해서입니다. 또한 본 작업의 수량이 많을 경우 잘못 만들어지면 클레임이나 분쟁의 소지가 있기 때문입니다. 이를 위해 샘플을 만들고 본 작업을 하는 경우도 많습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9e17645e-d2b8-4b75-acca-52314088e450\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c45028d1-30e0-437c-809f-8b974a1aa81d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-54f3e080-23f8-48bc-8351-fe395495d58d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a9cd19d3-53b3-4268-a09c-dd684d5975ae\" style=\"color:#555555;\">샘플을 잘 만들고 본 작업과 최대한 동일하게 만들어야 이 샘플을 보고 본 작업에 활용할 수 있기 때문에 반드시 샘플도 본 작업처럼 만들기를 추천드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-083d24ef-71e9-4bf2-a9cf-99f4db560151\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-257526a7-33f5-471f-8e6d-713127bc056b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-95f5e51d-ec29-4808-8720-301838b52dbd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2a9d97c4-ba6c-4280-a188-ee850d98c7ea\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 샘플뿐 아니라 표지싸바리 박스에 진심입니다. 거래 여부를 떠나 반드시 상담을 하시고 작업을 진행하시기 바랍니다. 꼼꼼히 체크하시지 않으면 나중에 문제가 발생됩니다. 꼭 문의하시고 진행하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}